<section class="py-5 mt-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">How we handle your data — GDPR compliant.</p>

    <div class="row mt-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <h2>Data Controller</h2>
        <p>{{content.dataController}}</p>
        <p>Contact: <a href="mailto:{{content.contactEmail}}">{{content.contactEmail}}</a></p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Data Collected</h2>
        <p>{{content.dataCollected}}</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Legal Basis</h2>
        <p>{{content.legalBasis}}</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>{{content.retentionPeriod}}</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Cookies and Analytics</h2>
        <p>{{content.cookiePolicy}}</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Session Cookies</h2>
        <p>If you register and log in, this website uses a single HTTP-only session cookie (<code>arthur_session</code>) to maintain your authenticated session. This cookie is strictly functional — it is not used for tracking, analytics, or advertising. The cookie expires after 1 hour of inactivity and is deleted when you log out.</p>

        <h2 class="mt-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request restriction of processing</li>
          <li>Data portability</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:{{content.contactEmail}}">{{content.contactEmail}}</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
